client smoothness:
  - smooth player movement on client side, it should not be jerky or laggy
  - server is running on its own tick but client should be able to handle it
  - no capping on client fps
  - client updates frequency = constant rate
  - client frame time = depend on client fps 
  - clients handles the current client simulation
  - sends the inputs to server
  - server updates the game state
  - in regular intervals the server sends the client state (authoritative)
  - client reconciles the server state with its own state
